::KitKat::

She walked to the entrance and looked outside.  She saw the two bots walk 
off together.  She yawned and looked back to the inside of the base.  She 
knew she didn't belong.  She wished her old pack was still alive.  But she 
made it and they didn't.  She looked back outside remembered days of hunting 
with the pack. Growing up with the pack rules. She longed to hunt again.  It 
had bee a while since she hunted.  She sniffed the air, she could smell 
another wolf.  Oh well, she thought, this isn't a pack society. She smiled 
at a few memories of her pack. She went back inside and walked around.
